description: One month away from his bodybuilding competition, Zack comes back to show us his progress. Amazing! In a post-interview, he admits that sex and bodybuilding both hold an important place in his life. Zack is known for being very at ease with his sexuality and with others. Once again, he gives an amazing performance that will please his fans and everybody who loves hot jocks. Zack will undoubtedly be a front runner in his upcoming competition!
title: One On One With Zack, Scene #01
